subject: Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Andrew Wiggins, the Big 12 freshman of the year, has propped the Jayhawks on his slender shoulders with Joel Embiid, a lithe 7-footer from Cameroon, out indefinitely with a stress fracture in his back.
